Title: An Act to Change the Name of Eulogio Rodriguez Elementary School Unit 1 Located at the Municipality of Mandaluyong, Metro Manila, to Andres Bonifacio Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 769
An Act to Change the Name of Eulogio Rodriguez Elementary School Unit 1 Located at the Municipality of Mandaluyong, Metro Manila, to Andres Bonifacio Elementary School
Section 1. Eulogio Rodriguez Elementary School Unit 1 located at the Municipality of Mandaluyong, Metro Manila, is hereby renamed Andres Bonifacio Elementary School in honor of one of the heroes of the Philippine Revolution, Andres Bonifacio.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
